actions.message:
**>ban [@user] [reason] - Bans a mentioned user and applies a reason for the ban

>kick [@user] [reason] - Kicks a mentioned user and applies a reason for the kick

>warn [@user] [reason] - Adds a warning point to mentioned user, will notify when a user has reached over 4 warns.

>setwarns [@user] [amount] - Sets a users warning points to a specific amount.

>inf [@user] [amount] - Allows you to view the amount of warning points a specific user has.**
